{"tid":962703,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"為 iPhone 4 賣腎!當年的青年事主現在怎樣?","createTime":"2018-12-31T05:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T06:42:18.000Z","uid":9826,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"93b73623beced8c8620b22cdc981e00a7e969db5","tid":962703,"uid":9826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:28:19.000Z","msg":"一說到 iPhone,因為多次改變世界,受到不少人歡迎,為了購買革命性的產品 iPhone 4,當年有人因此售賣自己的腎臟,換取金錢購買 iPhone,因此「腎」就成為了 iPhone 的代名詞,到底現在這位賣腎的少年情況如何呢?現在就有最新的消息.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/100608_apple_iphone4_cover_cover.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F100608_apple_iphone4_cover_cover.jpg&h=6093519d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nlivedoor 報導,故事的主角青年王先生,現在已經基本殘廢,因為當時賣腎的手術進行時的環境問題,沒有得到適當的消毒,導致傷口感染,直到最後才跟自己的父母解釋,如今只能躺在病床上,而由於消毒不到位,目前他的腎功能早已損壞.隨後這件事得到警方協助破案,拿到了補償,但是一生只能在床上度過了.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/2cd11_196_7d250384_47efff5c-e1546178308248.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F2cd11_196_7d250384_47efff5c-e1546178308248.jpg&h=2eb08892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實只是一台智能手機,是身外物,沒有足夠的金錢,那就不要購買吧,通過賣腎,這位青年拿到了2萬2千元人民幣,買到了iPhone 4,但最後卻得到這樣的結果,是無法挽回的.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/514_1_18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F514_1_18.jpg&h=b9f15494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/12/30/sell-iphone-4-mr-wong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F12%2F30%2Fsell-iphone-4-mr-wong%2F&d=Vzlor4zzsfsTuJsoLHP5MTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=b0c63f84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/12/30/sell-iphone-4-mr-wong/</a>"},{"pid":"0709a9f29454c3d5a128ebdfce5c5bc93e0a799c","tid":962703,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:29:49.000Z","msg":"教主罪孽太深 所以咁早死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錢無命享"},{"pid":"974b54e78da2681ad5963a5c7bf12d8e45c504d3","tid":962703,"uid":210161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:46:12.000Z","msg":"屌 單新聞單單係香港都出左五六日啦起碼<br />\n開咩鬼野post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6083dad971c36abc26973227993d2aae0ba615","tid":962703,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:19:55.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩"},{"pid":"4cc0f181983f6a4601ff56b3159d568abca5340e","tid":962703,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:42:18.000Z","msg":"香港代表<br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/c/c2/1295807992.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20110127110808\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fc%2Fc2%2F1295807992.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20110127110808&h=c6ceac45&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}